<concept id="cgsinsta" xml:lang="en-us">
<title>Installing and configuring Derby</title>
<shortdesc>This section will help you install and configure <ph conref="../conrefs.dita#prod/productshortname"></ph>.</shortdesc>
<conbody>
<p>After you complete the installation: <ul>
<li>Access the <xref href="cgstutorialintro.dita#cgstutorialintro">Self-study
tutorial</xref> to get up and running with Derby. This tutorial demonstrates
how to use <ph conref="../conrefs.dita#prod/productshortname"></ph> in the
embedded and client/server configurations.</li>
<li>If you are an experienced JDBC programmer, you should also see the <xref
href="cgsquck19524.dita#cgsquck19524"></xref>.</li>
</ul></p>
</conbody>
